title: Can see recent match history
body:
I was trying to check my match history for the game I had just played and it wouldn't appear. Please tell me i'm not the only one experiencing these problems...

THANKS

replies.body:
Hey there,

[This issue should now be resolved](http://boards.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support-oce/naMxWjok-match-history-not-showing-up?comment=0001), have your matches appeared?

Yes thank you{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}} , I can now see mine and others match results.

Do you have any idea to what had caused it?
